Backed by 46 years of experience accumulated since its inaugural event, Electra Mining Africa is seen as a gateway into Africa. The show continues to win favour with Africa’s mining and related industries and will be offering even more this year with over 900 exhibitors, showcasing the latest innovations, technologies and trends. It’s much more than a show – it’s a tradition - and this year there is more value for our visitors than ever before, Specialised Exhibitions Montgomery MD Gary Corin tells Sascha Solomons. This article first appeared in Mining Review Africa Issue 8 2018. It will be published online on the 7th September 2018. You can read the full digital magazine here or subscribe here to receive a print copy